    },
    "The handoff draft is missing required context for current runtime pressure.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前交接草稿缺少与运行时压力对应的必要上下文。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The handoff draft is usable, but some operator context is still thin.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前交接草稿可用，但值班员上下文仍然偏薄。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The requested agent is not available in the current dashboard snapshot.": {
      "comment": "An error message indicating that a requested agent is not available in the current dashboard snapshot.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请求的智能体在当前仪表盘快照中不可用。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "要求されたエージェントは現在のダッシュボードスナップショットでは利用できません。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The watched agent is no longer available in the current monitoring snapshot.": {
      "comment": "An alert message displayed when a user tries to access the details of an agent that is no longer in the current monitoring snapshot.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前监控快照中已找不到这个关注代理。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These agents are running but have not reported activity for at least 30 minutes.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这些智能体正在运行，但至少 30 分钟未上报活动。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これらのエージェントは稼働中ですが、少なくとも 30 分間アクティビティを報告していません。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These commands affect the active session on the server. Use them after confirming the current agent state.": {
      "comment": "A footer explaining the purpose of the session controls in the `AgentDetailView`.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这些命令会影响服务器上的当前活跃会话。请在确认代理当前状态后再使用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These filters are applied on top of the agent profile and determine which tools the runtime can actually call.": {
      "comment": "A footer text for the \"Tool Filters\" section of the AgentCapabilitiesView.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这些过滤器叠加在智能体配置档之上，并决定运行时实际可调用哪些工具。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These handoff signals are local to this iPhone and help keep operator follow-through visible inside the incident flow.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这些交接信号仅保存在这台 iPhone 上，用于在事故流中保持操作跟进可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これらの引き継ぎシグナルはこの iPhone ローカルのもので、インシデントの流れの中でオペレーターの追従を見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These warnings come from the kernel config validator and usually explain drift before it becomes an outage.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这些告警来自内核配置校验器，通常会在故障发生前解释漂移原因。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これらの警告はカーネル設定バリデーターからのもので、通常は障害になる前のドリフトを説明します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This agent has no recent outbound delivery receipts.": {
      "comment": "A description displayed when an agent has no recent outbound delivery receipts.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这个代理最近没有出站投递回执。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このエージェントには最近の送信配信レシートがありません。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This agent has not stored any KV entries yet.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这个代理还没有存储任何 KV 条目。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This agent is no longer present in the current monitoring snapshot.": {
      "comment": "A message displayed when a user navigates to the detail view of an agent that is no longer in the current monitoring snapshot.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
