      }
    },
    "This is already the active session.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这已经是当前活跃会话。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This is the read-only manifest snapshot from LibreFang. Use it to compare runtime behavior against fallback routing and capability grants.": {
      "comment": "A footer description under the \"Config Snapshot\" section in the agent detail view, explaining its purpose.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这是来自 LibreFang 的只读清单快照。可用于对比运行时行为与回退路由、能力授权之间的差异。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This is the redacted runtime config view from the server, not local iPhone settings.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这是来自服务器的脱敏运行时配置视图，不是本地 iPhone 设置。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これはローカルの iPhone 設定ではなく、サーバー由来のマスク済み runtime 設定ビューです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This section focuses on model providers, delivery channels, and the model catalog rather than runtime execution.": {
      "comment": "A footer label under the \"Integrations\" section of the runtime view, explaining its focus.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此区域聚焦模型提供方、投递渠道和模型目录，而不是运行时执行本身。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このセクションはランタイム実行ではなく、モデルプロバイダ、配信チャネル、モデルカタログに焦点を当てています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This section surfaces daemon-level health and build drift that the higher-level monitoring cards can miss.": {
      "comment": "A footer label explaining the purpose of the \"Diagnostics\" section in the Runtime view.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此区域会展示上层监控卡可能漏掉的守护进程级健康状态和构建漂移。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This shows the MCP server scope that the daemon exposes to the agent after runtime discovery.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这里展示守护进程在运行时发现后向智能体暴露的 MCP 服务范围。"
