    "Watchlist-focused handoff. Prioritize pinned agents, pending approvals, and any stale sessions.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "关注列表交接。优先处理置顶智能体、待处理审批和任何过期会话。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When a new critical incident appears while the app is open, show a temporary cue and haptic.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当应用处于前台且出现新的严重事故时，显示临时提示并触发震动。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "アプリを開いている間に新しい重大インシデントが現れたら、一時的なキューと触覚フィードバックを表示します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When agents start messaging, spawning, or coordinating tasks, their topology appears here.": {
      "comment": "A description of what the \"Topology\" section of the Comms view displays when there are no active links between agents.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当智能体开始发消息、生成子任务或协调任务时，它们的拓扑会显示在这里。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "エージェントがメッセージ送信、起動、またはタスク調整を始めると、そのトポロジがここに表示されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Widen the scope or wait for the next dashboard refresh.": {
      "comment": "A description text displayed when there are no automation items to display, and the user is not currently refreshing the data.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请扩大筛选范围，或等待下一次仪表盘刷新。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Workflow failures, exhausted triggers, and stalled cron jobs now flow into the mobile incident queue.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "工作流失败、触发器耗尽和停滞的定时任务现在都会进入移动端事故队列。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ワークフロー失敗、上限到達トリガー、停止中 Cron ジョブがモバイルのインシデントキューに流れ込むようになりました。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Workflow runs, triggers, schedules, and cron jobs are visible without active scheduler pressure.": {
      "comment": "A description of the benefits of having no active scheduler pressure.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "工作流运行、触发器、调度和定时任务已可见，当前没有活跃的调度压力。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ワークフロー実行、トリガー、スケジュール、cron ジョブは表示されていますが、現在スケジューラ負荷はありません。"
          }
        }
