        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "連携圧力は現在、チャネル設定ギャップとカタログ可用性に集中しています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Integration pressure is currently low and mostly reflects scope, search, and catalog breadth.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "集成压力当前较低，主要反映范围、搜索和目录广度。"
