            "value": "当前事件支持覆盖已被活动风险范围或搜索范围收窄。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "イベントサポートカバレッジは現在、有効な重大度または検索範囲によって絞り込まれています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Feed": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "事件流"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フィード"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Feed coverage": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "事件流概览"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フィードカバレッジ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Feed coverage keeps the active severity mix readable before the event rows begin.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "事件流概览会在事件行开始前保持当前风险分布清晰。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フィードカバレッジは、イベント行が始まる前に現在の重大度構成を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Filter by risk first, then use agent, tool, or action search only when the queue is still too broad.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "先按风险过滤，只有当队列仍然过宽时再按代理、工具或操作搜索。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "まずリスクで絞り込み、その後キューがまだ広すぎる場合にのみエージェント、ツール、または操作で検索します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Filtered by \\\"\\(query)\\\" before the event list.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "事件列表前已按“\\(query)”过滤。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "イベント一覧の前に「\\(query)」で絞り込まれています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Full queue": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完整队列"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フルキュー"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Immediate exits": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "即时出口"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "即時導線"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Jump straight to incidents, runtime, sessions, diagnostics, or comms without another long route stack.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "无需再展开长路由栈，就能直接跳转到事件、运行时、会话、诊断或通信。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "長いルート群をもう一段開かずに、インシデント、ランタイム、セッション、診断、通信へ直接移動できます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep decision pressure, agent spread, and visible tool breadth readable before acting on the queue.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在处理队列前，保持决策压力、代理分布和可见工具广度清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "キューを処理する前に、判断圧力、エージェント分布、表示中のツール範囲を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep deeper diagnostics and comms context behind the primary event routes.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "将更深层的诊断和通信上下文放在主要事件路由之后。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "より深い診断と通信の文脈は主要なイベントルートの後ろに置きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep event severity, result volume, and transport state visible before the feed rows take over.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在事件流行接管前，保持事件风险、结果量和传输状态可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フィード行が主役になる前に、イベント重大度、結果量、転送状態を見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep feed scope and event pressure visible before pivoting into incidents, runtime, sessions, diagnostics, or comms.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在切换到事件、运行时、会话、诊断或通信前，保持事件流范围和事件压力可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "インシデント、ランタイム、セッション、診断、通信へ切り替える前に、フィード範囲とイベント圧力を見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep overlay coverage readable before the quick-action rails and pressure badges.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在快捷操作轨和压力徽章前，保持浮层覆盖清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "クイックアクション列や圧力バッジの前に、オーバーレイのカバレッジを読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep overlay route breadth, snapshot state, and follow-up readiness visible before opening the primary and support exits.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在打开主出口和支持出口前，保持浮层路由广度、快照状态和后续跟进准备度可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "プライマリ導線とサポート導線を開く前に、オーバーレイルートの広さ、スナップショット状態、フォローアップ準備度を見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep queue breadth, agent spread, and tool mix visible before the approval rows and action buttons take over.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在审批行和操作按钮接管前，保持队列广度、代理分布和工具组合可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "承認行と操作ボタンが主役になる前に、キューの広さ、エージェント分布、ツール構成を見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep queue coverage, agent spread, and tool load visible before the approval rows take over.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在审批行接管前，保持队列覆盖、代理分布和工具负载可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "承認行が主役になる前に、キューカバレッジ、エージェント分布、ツール負荷を見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep queue severity, agent spread, and visible results clear before acting on requests from the phone.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在手机上处理请求前，保持队列风险、代理分布和可见结果清晰。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "この端末から要求に対応する前に、キューの重大度、エージェント分布、表示中の結果を明確に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep route breadth, filter scope, and visible approval spread readable before leaving the approval queue for broader operator context.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在离开审批队列进入更广运维上下文前，保持路由广度、过滤范围和可见审批分布清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "より広いオペレータ文脈へ移る前に、ルートの広さ、フィルタ範囲、表示中の承認分布を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep severity pressure, transport mode, and visible slice breadth readable before drilling into the audit feed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在深入审计流前，保持风险压力、传输模式和可见切片范围清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "監査フィードを深掘りする前に、重大度圧力、転送モード、表示中の断面の広さを読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep severity scope, transport mode, and audit pressure readable before opening the full feed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在打开完整事件流前，保持风险范围、传输模式和审计压力清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完全なフィードを開く前に、重大度範囲、転送モード、監査圧力を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep severity, routes, and filters together before the approval list.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在审批列表前，将风险、路由和过滤器集中展示。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "承認一覧の前に、重大度、ルート、フィルタをまとめて表示します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep supporting diagnostics and session drilldowns close when the overlay is carrying secondary pressure.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当浮层承载次级压力时，将辅助诊断和会话下钻保持在附近。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オーバーレイが二次的な圧力を抱えているときは、補助的な診断やセッション深掘りを近くに置きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep tab-level pressure readable before jumping into the next monitor surface.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在跳转到下一个监控面板前，保持标签级压力清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "次の監視面へ移動する前に、タブ単位の圧力を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the incident, on-call, and runtime exits closest to approval review.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "将事件、值守和运行时出口放在最靠近审批审核的位置。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "インシデント、オンコール、ランタイムへの導線を承認レビューの近くに置きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the next queue and runtime exits closest to the event feed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "将下一步队列和运行时出口放在最靠近事件流的位置。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "次のキューとランタイムへの導線をイベントフィードの近くに置きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the preferred surface and quick-action split readable before opening the full monitor surface.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在打开完整监控面板前，保持首选面板和快捷操作分区清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完全な監視面を開く前に、優先サーフェスとクイックアクションの分割を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the preferred surface, urgent drilldowns, and supporting operator exits reachable from the overlay without expanding the full monitoring stack.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "无需展开完整监控栈，也能从浮层中触达首选面板、紧急下钻和辅助运维出口。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完全な監視スタックを開かなくても、オーバーレイから優先サーフェス、緊急ドリルダウン、補助オペレータ導線へ到達できるようにします。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep transport mode and visible feed breadth readable before diving into individual audit rows.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在深入单条审计行前，保持传输模式和可见事件流范围清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "個々の監査行に入る前に、転送モードと表示中のフィード範囲を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep transport mode, info traffic, and scope state readable before the event feed expands into row-by-row audit detail.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在事件流展开为逐行审计细节前，保持传输模式、信息流量和范围状态清晰可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "イベントフィードが行単位の監査詳細へ広がる前に、転送モード、情報トラフィック、範囲状態を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep transport mode, scope, and route breadth visible before leaving the event feed for the surrounding monitor surfaces.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在离开事件流进入周边监控面板前，保持传输模式、范围和路由广度可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "周辺の監視面へ移る前に、転送モード、範囲、ルートの広さを見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Latest \\(RelativeDateTimeFormatter().localizedString(for: date, relativeTo: Date()))": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "最新 \\(RelativeDateTimeFormatter().localizedString(for: date, relativeTo: Date()))"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "最新 \\(RelativeDateTimeFormatter().localizedString(for: date, relativeTo: Date()))"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Live transport": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "实时传输"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ライブ転送"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Monitoring data may be stale while this iPhone is offline.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这台 iPhone 离线时，监控数据可能会过期。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "この iPhone がオフラインの間、監視データは古くなる可能性があります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Offline banner": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "离线横幅"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オフラインバナー"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Offline fallback": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "离线兜底"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オフライン代替導線"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open the on-call surface to inspect the latest pressure.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "打开值守面板以查看最新压力。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オンコール画面を開いて最新の圧力を確認してください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open the on-call surface to review the new state.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "打开值守面板以查看新的状态。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オンコール画面を開いて新しい状態を確認してください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Overlay action readiness is currently anchored by follow-up and muted-alert follow-through.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前浮层行动就绪度主要受后续跟进和已静音告警的后续处理影响。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オーバーレイのアクション準備度は現在、フォローアップとミュート済みアラートの後追い対応に左右されています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Overlay action readiness is currently anchored by offline recovery and fallback routes.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前浮层行动就绪度主要受离线恢复和兜底路由影响。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オーバーレイのアクション準備度は現在、オフライン回復と代替ルートに左右されています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Overlay action readiness is currently anchored by urgent exits from the active snapshot.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前浮层行动就绪度主要受活动快照中的紧急出口影响。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オーバーレイのアクション準備度は現在、アクティブなスナップショットからの緊急導線に左右されています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Overlay action readiness is currently centered on the preferred surface and nearby operator exits.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前浮层行动就绪度主要取决于首选面板和附近的运维出口。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オーバーレイのアクション準備度は現在、優先サーフェスと近くのオペレータ導線が中心です。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Overlay routes are currently anchored by counted live signals from the top monitor surfaces.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前浮层路由主要受顶层监控面的带计数实时信号影响。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オーバーレイルートは現在、上位監視面からの件数付きライブシグナルに左右されています。"
