            "state": "translated",
            "value": "さらに深掘りする前に、ダイジェスト、ルート、ジャンプをまとめて表示します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the dominant runtime lane readable before moving from compact status decks into deeper feeds, queues, and route groups.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在从紧凑状态卡片切换到更深的 feed、队列和路由组前，保持主导的运行时通道清晰可读。"
          }
