        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "キューに入る前に、インシデントコントロールは \\(primaryRouteCount) 件の主要ルートと \\(supportRouteCount) 件の補助ルートをまとめています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Incident focus coverage is currently anchored by handoff and watched-diagnostics follow-through.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
