          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open the dedicated session monitor when hotspots spread beyond the compact incident list.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当热点扩散到紧凑事件列表之外时，打开专用会话监视器。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ホットスポットがコンパクトなインシデント一覧を超えて広がったら、専用のセッションモニターを開きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open the full event feed when the compact critical trail needs deeper inspection.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当紧凑的严重轨迹需要更深入检查时，打开完整事件流。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "コンパクトな重大トレイルをさらに詳しく確認する必要がある場合、完全なイベントフィードを開きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open the full fleet monitor when agent pressure spreads beyond the top incident rows.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当代理压力扩散到顶部事件行之外时，打开完整机群监视器。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "エージェント負荷が上部のインシデント行を超えて広がったら、完全なフリートモニターを開きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pinned agents can stay visible here even when they would otherwise drop out of the normal fleet attention list.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "即使已固定代理本应从常规机群关注列表中退出，也可以继续显示在这里。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ピン留めしたエージェントは、通常のフリート注意一覧から外れる状態でもここに表示し続けられます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Primary Queue Sections": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主队列分区"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主要キューセクション"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Primary buckets keep the operator loop near the top, while support buckets hold slower diagnostics and fleet follow-up.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主分桶会让操作环路靠近顶部，而辅助分桶则承载较慢的诊断和机群跟进。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主要バケットはオペレーターループを上部近くに保ち、補助バケットは遅い診断やフリートのフォローアップを受け持ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Primary exits stay biased toward the next likely triage surfaces, while support exits keep deeper runtime context nearby.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主出口会偏向下一步最可能的分诊界面，而辅助出口则让更深层的运行时上下文保持在附近。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主要出口は次に可能性の高いトリアージ画面へ寄り、補助出口はより深いランタイム文脈を近くに保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Primary only": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "仅主分组"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主要のみ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Provider reachability, channel config gaps, catalog freshness, and drift stay compact before the larger integration drilldown.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在进入更大的集成下钻之前，提供方可达性、通道配置缺口、目录新鲜度和漂移会先以紧凑形式显示。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "より大きな統合ドリルダウンに入る前に、プロバイダ到達性、チャネル設定の欠落、カタログ鮮度、ドリフトがコンパクトにまとまります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Queue": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "队列"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "キュー"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Session Hotspots": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "会话热点"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "セッションホットスポット"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Supporting Queue Sections": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "辅助队列分区"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "補助キューセクション"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Targets": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "目标"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ターゲット"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The compact approval slice is currently dominated by standard-risk actions.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "紧凑审批切片当前主要由标准风险操作主导。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "コンパクトな承認スライスは現在、標準リスクのアクションが中心です。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The compact event slice stays focused on the newest critical trail before you open the full feed or diagnostics monitor.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在打开完整事件流或诊断监视器之前，紧凑事件切片会继续聚焦最新的严重轨迹。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完全なフィードや診断モニターを開く前に、コンパクトなイベントスライスは最新の重大トレイルに焦点を当て続けます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The compact session slice stays focused on the hottest rows before you jump into the broader session monitor.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在跳转到更广的会话监视器之前，紧凑会话切片会继续聚焦最热的行。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "より広いセッションモニターへ移る前に、コンパクトなセッションスライスはもっとも熱い行に焦点を当て続けます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The incident queue is showing \\(visibleCount) of \\(totalCount) pending approvals.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "事件队列当前显示 \\(visibleCount) / \\(totalCount) 个待处理审批。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "インシデントキューには現在、\\(totalCount) 件中 \\(visibleCount) 件の保留承認が表示されています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The incident queue is showing \\(visibleCount) of \\(totalCount) watched diagnostic issues.": {
