    "Nothing is hidden below the fold, so the standby queue is fully represented in the glance deck.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "折叠下方没有隐藏内容，因此待命队列已在概览卡片中完整呈现。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
