    },
    "Standby Snapshot": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待命快照"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待機スナップショット"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Standby is grouping \\(primaryRouteCount) primary routes and \\(supportRouteCount) support routes in one calm control deck.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待命会在一个平静控制卡片中分组显示 \\(primaryRouteCount) 个主路由和 \\(supportRouteCount) 个辅助路由。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待機では、\\(primaryRouteCount) 件の主要ルートと \\(supportRouteCount) 件の補助ルートを 1 つの落ち着いたコントロールデッキにまとめています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Standby keeps the top queue, muted pressure, and handoff follow-ups visible while the phone stays calm.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在手机保持平静时，待命会让顶部队列、静音压力和交接跟进保持可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "端末が落ち着いている間、待機では上位キュー、ミュート負荷、引き継ぎフォローを見えるまま保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Standby support coverage is currently anchored by handoff follow-up and check-in context.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待命辅助覆盖当前由交接跟进和签到上下文主导。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待機の補助カバレッジは現在、引き継ぎフォローとチェックイン文脈が軸です。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Standby support coverage is currently anchored by local watch breadth and live alert visibility.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待命辅助覆盖当前由本地监视广度和实时告警可见性主导。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待機の補助カバレッジは現在、ローカル監視の幅とライブアラートの可視性が軸です。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Standby support coverage is currently light and mostly reflects local standby readiness.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待命辅助覆盖当前较轻，主要反映本地待命就绪度。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待機の補助カバレッジは現在軽く、主にローカル待機の準備状況を反映しています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Support Pressure": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "辅助压力"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "補助負荷"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Surfaces": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "界面"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "サーフェス"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The first rail keeps the next live drills close, while the support rail holds slower background and sharing surfaces.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "第一条栏位会让下一步实时下钻保持靠近，而辅助栏则承载较慢的后台与共享界面。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "最初のレールは次のライブドリルを近くに保ち、補助レールはより遅いバックグラウンドと共有画面を受け持ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The glance deck is holding the sharpest standby slice while \\(remainingCount) lower-priority cards stay below.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "概览卡片承载了最尖锐的待命切片，而 \\(remainingCount) 张较低优先级卡片会保留在下方。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "グランスデッキにはもっとも鋭い待機スライスが載っており、\\(remainingCount) 件の低優先カードは下に残ります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The top standby slice stays compact so queue pressure, muted alerts, and follow-ups remain readable on a locked-down phone.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "顶部待命切片会保持紧凑，以便在受限手机上仍能读清队列压力、静音告警和后续事项。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "上位の待機スライスはコンパクトなまま保たれ、制約のある端末でもキュー負荷、ミュートアラート、フォローアップを読みやすくします。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This agent is no longer present in the current snapshot.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这个代理已不再出现在当前快照中。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このエージェントは現在のスナップショットにはもう存在しません。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Top slice is full": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "顶部切片已满"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "上位スライスは満杯です"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use the compact route inventory to decide whether standby should escalate into night watch, on-call, or a slower support drill.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用紧凑路由清单判断待命是否应升级为夜间值守、值班或较慢的辅助下钻。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "コンパクトなルートインベントリを使って、待機をナイトウォッチ、オンコール、または遅い補助ドリルへ昇格させるべきか判断します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use this deck to keep local watch breadth, live alert visibility, and slower handoff support context readable before the readiness deck and route rails expand.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用此卡片，在就绪卡片和路由栏展开前，让本地监视广度、实时告警可见性和较慢的交接辅助上下文保持可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このデッキで、準備デッキとルートレールが広がる前に、ローカル監視の幅、ライブアラートの可視性、遅い引き継ぎ補助の文脈を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
