    "Filter active": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "筛选激活"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フィルター有効"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep broader runtime context behind the primary delivery path.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "让更广的运行时上下文位于主要投递路径之后。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "より広いランタイム文脈は主要な配信経路の後ろに置きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep delivered, failed, and unsettled receipt support readable before moving into incidents, events, or runtime context.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在切换到事件、审计或运行时上下文前，先让已送达、失败和未结清的回执辅助保持可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "インシデント、イベント、またはランタイムの文脈へ移る前に、配信済み、失敗、未解決のレシート補助を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep delivery failure, settlement lag, and freshness readable before the outbound receipt rows take over.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在外发回执行接管前，先让投递失败、结算滞后和新鲜度保持可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "送信レシート行が前面に出る前に、配信失敗、解決の遅れ、鮮度を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep failed, unsettled, and delivered receipt lanes readable before moving through the full outbound receipt log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在浏览完整外发回执日志前，先让失败、未结清和已送达的回执通道保持可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完全な送信レシートログをたどる前に、失敗、未解決、配信済みのレシートレーンを読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep nearby agent, incident, audit, and runtime exits closest to delivery failures and unsettled receipts.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "让附近的代理、事件、审计和运行时出口最靠近投递失败与未结清回执。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "近くのエージェント、インシデント、監査、ランタイムの出口を、配信失敗と未解決レシートの近くに置きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep summary, routes, and receipt coverage visible before drilling into the full outbound delivery log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在深入完整外发投递日志前，先让摘要、路由和回执覆盖保持可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完全な送信配信ログへ掘り下げる前に、要約、ルート、レシートカバレッジを見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the active scope, channel spread, dominant delivery lane, and latest receipt timing visible while scanning delivery history.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在扫描投递历史时，先让激活范围、通道分布、主投递通道和最新回执时间保持可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "配信履歴を確認する間、アクティブな範囲、チャネル分布、主要な配信レーン、最新レシート時刻を見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the agent, current scope, and freshest receipt timing available while filtering receipt history.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在筛选回执历史时，保持代理、当前范围和最新回执时间可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "レシート履歴を絞り込む間、エージェント、現在の範囲、最新レシート時刻を見えるままにします。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the dominant delivery lane readable before moving from compact delivery decks into receipt rows and adjacent incident routes.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在从紧凑投递卡片切换到回执行和相邻事件路由前，先让主投递通道保持可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "コンパクトな配信デッキからレシート行と隣接するインシデントルートへ移る前に、主要な配信レーンを読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the next receipt stack visible before delivery rows expand into the full outbound log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在投递行展开为完整外发日志前，先让下一组回执堆栈保持可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "配信行が完全な送信ログへ広がる前に、次のレシートスタックを見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep visible receipt size and unsettled delivery pressure readable before pivoting into agent, incident, events, or runtime context.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在切换到代理、事件、审计或运行时上下文前，先让可见回执规模和未结清投递压力保持可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "エージェント、インシデント、イベント、またはランタイムの文脈へ切り替える前に、表示中レシートの規模と未解決配信負荷を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Receipt Facts": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "回执概况"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "レシート要点"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Recent outbound receipts stay summarized before the longer delivery log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在更长的投递日志之前，最近的外发回执会保持摘要显示。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "より長い配信ログの前で、最近の送信レシートは要約表示されたままです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Scoped inventory": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "限定范围清单"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "絞り込みインベントリ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Section coverage stays visible before routes and the longer receipt log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在路由和更长的回执日志之前，分区覆盖会保持可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ルートとより長いレシートログの前で、セクションカバレッジは見えるまま保たれます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Section coverage stays visible while delivery receipts are still loading.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当投递回执仍在加载时，分区覆盖会保持可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "配信レシートの読み込み中も、セクションカバレッジは見えるまま保たれます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The active delivery slice stays compact before the full receipt list.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在完整回执列表之前，激活的投递切片会保持紧凑。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "アクティブな配信スライスは完全なレシート一覧の前でコンパクトなままです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The filtered delivery slice stays compact before the full receipt list.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在完整回执列表之前，筛选后的投递切片会保持紧凑。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フィルター済みの配信スライスは完全なレシート一覧の前でコンパクトなままです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This surface keeps outbound delivery state visible before any receipts load.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这个界面会在任何回执加载前让外发投递状态保持可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "この画面は、レシートが 1 件も読み込まれる前に送信配信状態を見えるまま保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use nearby incident and audit surfaces first.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "优先使用附近的事件与审计界面。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "まず近くのインシデントと監査の画面を使ってください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use section coverage to confirm how much delivery context is ready before leaving receipt inspection.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用分区覆盖确认离开回执检查前已有多少投递上下文准备就绪。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "セクションカバレッジを使って、レシート確認を離れる前にどれだけの配信文脈が準備できているか確認します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use section coverage to confirm the active receipt scope before pivoting into nearby incident or runtime surfaces.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用分区覆盖确认激活的回执范围后，再切换到附近的事件或运行时界面。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "近くのインシデントまたはランタイム画面へ切り替える前に、セクションカバレッジでアクティブなレシート範囲を確認します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use the deck to gauge channel spread, recent failures, and unsettled sends before opening each receipt row.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用此卡片，在打开每个回执行前判断通道分布、近期失败和未结清发送。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このデッキで、各レシート行を開く前にチャネル分布、最近の失敗、未解決送信を見極めます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use the route deck when delivery receipts need incident, audit, or runtime context.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当投递回执需要事件、审计或运行时上下文时，使用路由卡片。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "配信レシートにインシデント、監査、またはランタイムの文脈が必要な場合は、ルートデッキを使います。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use the route inventory to gauge the visible receipt slice before leaving delivery inspection.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用路由清单，在离开投递检查前判断可见回执切片。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ルートインベントリを使って、配信確認を離れる前に表示中のレシートスライスを見極めます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use these routes when delivery receipts need incident, event, or runtime context.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当投递回执需要事件、审计或运行时上下文时，使用这些路由。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "配信レシートにインシデント、イベント、またはランタイムの文脈が必要な場合は、これらのルートを使います。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use this deck to keep delivery confirmation, failure support, and the freshest receipt timing readable before leaving the outbound receipt log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用此卡片，在离开外发回执日志前，让投递确认、失败辅助和最新回执时间保持可读。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このデッキで、送信レシートログを離れる前に、配信確認、失敗補助、最新レシート時刻を読みやすく保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use this deck to keep the dominant delivery lane visible before opening route rails and the full receipt log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用此卡片，在打开路由栏和完整回执日志前，让主投递通道保持可见。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このデッキで、ルートレールと完全なレシートログを開く前に、主要な配信レーンを見える状態に保ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use this deck to see whether delivery review is currently led by failed receipts, unsettled receipts, or confirmed outbound traffic before the log opens.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用此卡片，在日志展开前查看当前投递审查是由失败回执、未结清回执还是已确认的外发流量主导。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このデッキで、ログが開く前に現在の配信確認が失敗レシート、未解決レシート、または確認済み送信トラフィックのどれに主導されているかを確認します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use this deck to separate confirmed delivery, failed sends, unsettled receipts, and scoped receipt slices before opening the full log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用此卡片，在打开完整日志前区分已确认投递、失败发送、未结清回执和限定范围的回执切片。"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このデッキで、完全なログを開く前に確認済み配信、失敗送信、未解決レシート、絞り込みレシートスライスを切り分けます。"
          }
        }
